ware enclave (e.g., Apple's Secure Enclave, Intel SGX). Even if the host OS=
 is compromised, the attacker cannot see or tamper with the agent's interna=
l state.</p></li></ol><h2 data-path-to-node=3D"26">Technical Claims for Int=
