ata-index-in-node=3D"0">A "Black Box" Record (Blockchain):</b> It creates a=
 permanent, unchangeable "receipt" of <i data-path-to-node=3D"6,0,0,0" data=
-index-in-node=3D"85">why</i> the agent made a decision, using the agent's =
