he plan mid-task.</p><p data-path-to-node=3D"1">Here is the detailed, step-=
by-step flow of how the system knows your original intention and uses it to=
 block a phishing attack.</p><h3 data-path-to-node=3D"2">Step-by-Step Flow:=
