index-in-node=3D"0">Semantic Similarity:</b> It asks: <i data-path-to-node=
=3D"14,1,0" data-index-in-node=3D"30">"Is reading the user's password file =
related to finding a bank rate?"</i></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=3D"14=
